From b5d2e79f6b40bc75ffdd30296a8559f37b1bdf08 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Thu, 23 Jul 2026 09:30:11 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 4/6] Restyle dark theme to a moodier navy/slate palette, add
 Inter/Space Grotesk/JetBrains Mono fonts, shrink the news ticker

Fonts are now loaded app-wide (Inter for body text, Space Grotesk for
bold headings via inline fontWeight:800, JetBrains Mono for existing
monospace usages) in both themes. Only dark-theme colors were adjusted;
light theme keeps its palette.
